Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H534D4D&\fs30\bord0\pos(423.771,339)\frz346.6}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說夏目在找你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,森川說的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那你別逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我還沒有贏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.36,0:15:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我還沒有贏過陽斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們就比比吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,今天瑛太你拿這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.97,0:15:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你打個全壘打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,去啊
